nodes.text: Anders was a Human male corporal who served the Galactic Republic during the Galactic War against the resurgent Sith Empire.

Around 3641 BBY, Captain Trey-yen and Corporal Anders led a strike team on the planet Quesh to place explosives in order to bring down an Imperial outpost from down below. When the Darth Baras' apprentice interrupted the men, Anders asked to Sith to let them go, but Trey-yen decided to detonate the explosives anyway in order to destroy themselves the Sith Lord. However, the bomb failed to detonate and the Sith Warrior proceeded to kill Anders and the rest.
